{"tid":1916500,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"泰國宣佈入境隔離14日政策 包括中港澳韓","createTime":"2020-03-09T02:03:21.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-09T04:51:13.000Z","uid":23707,"like":18,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":27,"replies":[{"pid":"9a12ac6cf469dfc0320cc3581e4895a41eab8b51","tid":1916500,"uid":23707,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-09T02:03:21.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />今次堅"},{"pid":"d899b8110cc6581f9096f4057fc6fb8759c2f2d3","tid":1916500,"uid":36178,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-09T02:04:55.000Z","msg":"上次都堅"},{"pid":"5008a1e0ba4f65ae675613ff1dcb2a3b7273f364","tid":1916500,"uid":48603,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-09T02:06:22.000Z","msg":"彈出彈入n次<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ade693e5384162f07379e51a63ee0ac3da363a5e","tid":1916500,"uid":17646,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"5008a1e0ba4f65ae675613ff1dcb2a3b7273f364","tid":1916500,"uid":48603,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-09T02:06:22.000Z","msg":"彈出彈入n次<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-09T02:07:51.000Z","msg":"旅遊局同衛生局角力"},{"pid":"6d8633916af429cceca8e9714ca660ce7a5e0675","tid":1916500,"uid":113000,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-09T02:08:52.000Z","msg":"見到意大利爆到咁先識驚"},{"pid":"1ab6af02d59edecf1da28eef02f0de27f12cf820","tid":1916500,"uid":10637,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-09T02:09:03.000Z","msg":"Source?"},{"pid":"90b0c72669994b3b1fbcf991261a9e973c35fa36","tid":1916500,"uid":152222,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-03-09T02:10:31.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/wVywPc8.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FwVywPc8.jpg&h=975bca05&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"2ebb66bea7f450ccbe360fada289ab1f134039a8","tid":1916500,"uid":117673,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-09T02:17:09.000Z","msg":"source?"},{"pid":"9d4d29de2a17b17806c3f0caadbb9556355b92b8","tid":1916500,"uid":13663,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-09T02:19:45.000Z","msg":"入境限制】泰國實施入境隔離14日政策　包括中港澳韓等旅客<br />\n<br />\n泰國旅遊局宣布，因應新型冠狀病毒疫情最新發展，泰國政府將採取更嚴密的入境措施。所有由中國（包括香港和澳門）、南韓、意大利和伊朗的入境旅客均需要填健康申報，和進行14天的隔離。若抵泰旅客被發現有相關病徵，會即時轉介並接受更詳細檢疫測試。14天隔離的詳細安排會再作進一步更新。<br />\n<br />\n多個港人熱發的旅遊國相繼淪陷，港人入境也面臨限制，而泰國入境措拖堪稱近期最受關注。泰國入境安排多次「彈弓手」，泰國衛生部阿努廷（Anutin Charnvirakul）在Facebook發文稱，所有來自「高危地區」的人士，包括中國、南韓、日本和新加坡，都會被安排隔離。但帖文迅速被刪。翌日，泰國旅遊部的新加坡辦公室否認相關隔離安排。<br />\n<br />\n暫時得經濟日報"},{"pid":"fa8532707762c1475c379adac618e455bc91fbb3","tid":1916500,"uid":50101,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-09T02:20:36.000Z","msg":"跳出跳入國<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"be5a0809cb9b577379282d8e65354ba5ebcf0f5b","tid":1916500,"uid":14494,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"90b0c72669994b3b1fbcf991261a9e973c35fa36","tid":1916500,"uid":152222,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-03-09T02:10:31.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/wVywPc8.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FwVywPc8.jpg&h=975bca05&s={SIZE}\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-09T02:20:52.000Z","msg":"有冇全英文版<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7e206515ec0b6815fa585fc98aae2aa3e65cf15f","tid":1916500,"uid":63154,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-09T02:21:52.000Z","msg":"終於內部傾掂數<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e0e8b3a5557c39d80e627fd646a3eafcb61edc96","tid":1916500,"uid":250654,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-09T02:22:08.000Z","msg":"【新冠肺炎】泰國旅遊局實施入境隔離14日政策 包中港澳韓等旅客<br />\n<br />\n【09:20】香港泰國旅遊局宣布，因應新型冠狀病毒(covid-19)疫情最新發展，泰國政府將採取更嚴密的入境措施。所有由中國（包括香港和澳門）、南韓、意大利和伊朗的入境旅客均需要填健康申報，和進行14天的隔離。若抵泰旅客被發現有相關病徵，會即時轉介並接受更詳細檢疫測試。<br />\n<br />\nSource: 支那01"},{"pid":"7a144ceea5d809539cce9a3ec93559281a97a638","tid":1916500,"uid":171866,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-09T02:23:57.000Z","msg":"唔係強制其實=廢話"},{"pid":"732b74e0f9967acd2f1f4f182f315398b45ddbaf","tid":1916500,"uid":4811,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"90b0c72669994b3b1fbcf991261a9e973c35fa36","tid":1916500,"uid":152222,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-03-09T02:10:31.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/wVywPc8.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FwVywPc8.jpg&h=975bca05&s={SIZE}\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-09T02:24:22.000Z","msg":"正撚到爆，咁想上位一於幫佢宣揚開去"},{"pid":"056a7c779d09faff853a6311fc7ed1b18afb5245","tid":1916500,"uid":49643,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-09T02:24:34.000Z","msg":"成個歐洲都爆緊，而且都爆得比香港澳門勁，幾時封埋？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"18e3a62ada375f76ec9e4a71245f4e2b6b57174a","tid":1916500,"uid":152222,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"be5a0809cb9b577379282d8e65354ba5ebcf0f5b","tid":1916500,"uid":14494,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"90b0c72669994b3b1fbcf991261a9e973c35fa36","tid":1916500,"uid":152222,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-03-09T02:10:31.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/wVywPc8.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FwVywPc8.jpg&h=975bca05&s={SIZE}\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-09T02:20:52.000Z","msg":"有冇全英文版<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-09T02:25:23.000Z","msg":"上Twitter見到down的"},{"pid":"370a1ad2f28ce9a4c5238bd2f3ddf74a5f98dc48","tid":1916500,"uid":250654,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1ab6af02d59edecf1da28eef02f0de27f12cf820","tid":1916500,"uid":1